The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball
1. the person who likes blood-red is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Color   | blood-red | pink   |
| Sport         | skiing | volleyball |

